{"tid":1007362,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"同親戚食飯，老豆叫我爭埋單，結果我唔小心贏左","createTime":"2019-02-03T16:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T09:28:37.000Z","uid":228438,"like":56,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef346fcf1b2ce4189b455f12001e45f9218eeabe","tid":1007362,"uid":228438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:53:50.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩提早食團年飯<br />\n12個人飲食<br />\n1300$(計埋加二即係1302$) <br />\n<br />\n老豆叫我扮大方爭埋單，事敗後比100$獎金給我 <br />\n結果同桌的表哥爭都不爭就自動棄權 <br />\n話下次佢請返......局撚住我請 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞到我要即場拆利是 先夠錢比 <br />\n仲要無啦啦比酒樓屈多258$ <br />\n之後問返老豆拎錢 <br />\n點知佢話我大個仔要試下請親戚食飯既滋味 <br />\n愈諗愈唔對路，懷疑老豆夾我親戚屈我餐茶飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778ecb890dfc95f65a9b0183c7f342d77c1ca3b5","tid":1007362,"uid":38841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6248453&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6248453%26page%3D1&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=b6e030c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6248453&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"15b2f40c3a3ccd862a31825a4a304202da3fac04","tid":1007362,"uid":195364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"抄早左啦"},{"pid":"95b2b3130070d1982cb2f6380553c984e2887b0e","tid":1007362,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"778ecb890dfc95f65a9b0183c7f342d77c1ca3b5","tid":1007362,"uid":38841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6248453&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6248453%26page%3D1&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=b6e030c0\" target=\"_